{"tid":908931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【醫院槍擊】芝加哥急症室爆槍擊 1警員2醫院員工慘死","createTime":"2018-11-20T03:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T03:30:57.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7bb9de34cd3b8c2c6e07676edf4a21f807e5733b","tid":908931,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181120/large/1542666789_5c12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181120%2Flarge%2F1542666789_5c12.jpg&h=27b2976c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國芝加哥一名槍手周一在一間醫院槍傷4人，包括一名警員和兩名醫院職員，當地傳媒引述消息指3人經搶救後不治，餘下的1人亦情況危殆；此外，警方證實槍手死亡，未知他是自殺還是被擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n事發於慈愛醫院（Mercy Hospital）。當地傳媒報道，一名女子和一名警員先後在停車場和醫院內中槍。槍手可能也被開槍擊傷。<br />\n<br />\n傳媒引述目擊者表示，聽到多響槍聲，然後見到槍手向地上一人連開多槍，警員到場與槍手駁火，槍手向地上傷者開槍後走入醫院內，再連開多槍。<br />\n<br />\n當地電視台片段顯示，醫院內的人高舉雙手，疏散到院外停車場。<br />\n<br />\n美國霍士新聞／《紐約郵報》  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181120/large/1542667610_cf83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181120%2Flarge%2F1542667610_cf83.jpg&h=0fc9425b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">醫院內的人高舉雙手，疏散到停車場。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181120/58934535\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F58934535&d=6bPelPYNlKPQ9BKRbB%2BhvS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a1825716\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181120%2F58934535&h=04976b39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181120/58934535</a>"},{"pid":"737e3d17e99e3756307e6b5b88e793f60b463db2","tid":908931,"uid":97739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"慈愛醫院，LEFT 4 DEAD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa647670f72bec14accd738abf80fb99dc87814","tid":908931,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"737e3d17e99e3756307e6b5b88e793f60b463db2","tid":908931,"uid":97739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"慈愛醫院，LEFT 4 DEAD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f860b2e154812bd1961d1908ec9552c7cbfd0a","tid":908931,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"737e3d17e99e3756307e6b5b88e793f60b463db2","tid":908931,"uid":97739,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:23:55.000Z","msg":"慈愛醫院，LEFT 4 DEAD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/left4dead/images/1/18/Hospital.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20081201152637\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fleft4dead%2Fimages%2F1%2F18%2FHospital.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20081201152637&h=104bc7d2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}